Kam Fong Chun https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kam_Fong_Chun 0 Kam Fong Chun (May 27, 1918 – October 18, 2002), born Kam Tong Chun, was an American police officer and actor, best known for his role as Chin Ho Kelly, a police detective on the CBS television network series Hawaii Five-O.
